<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 13:01:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>价值 2.85 亿美元的加密货币黑客攻击和收益率下降震撼了 DeFi 行业</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/a-285-million-crypto-hack-and-falling-yields-rock-defi-industry</link><description>去中心化金融曾经是数字资产行业最具活力的领域之一，但现在几乎面临着来自各个方面的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibO5XwxGevLY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 12:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-16/a-285-million-crypto-hack-and-falling-yields-rock-defi-industry</guid></item><item><title>AI Pivot 推动比特币矿工迈向 70% 收入里程碑</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/ai-pivot-pushes-bitcoin-miners-toward-a-70-revenue-milestone</link><description>那些通过挖掘比特币建立了数十亿美元业务的公司有望在今年年底前从人工智能中获得大部分收入——这是一个里程碑，标志着整个行业正在远离创造它的加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCTlfqZu9sRo/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 15:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/ai-pivot-pushes-bitcoin-miners-toward-a-70-revenue-milestone</guid></item><item><title>EToro 将以 7000 万美元收购加密钱包初创公司 Zengo</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/etoro-etor-to-acquire-crypto-wallet-startup-zengo-in-70-million-deal</link><description>EToro Group Ltd. 已同意收购加密钱包提供商 Zengo，该交易和投资平台将其业务范围扩大到去中心化金融领域。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTsSrceD0r0I/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/etoro-etor-to-acquire-crypto-wallet-startup-zengo-in-70-million-deal</guid></item><item><title>法国兴业银行向数百万加密钱包用户提供美元稳定币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/socgen-takes-usd-stablecoin-to-millions-of-crypto-wallet-users</link><description>法国兴业银行正在扩大其以美元计价的稳定币的覆盖范围，这是大型银行迄今为止为将数字货币带给更广泛受众而做出的最大努力之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i26oRrVOKUds/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 06:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-15/socgen-takes-usd-stablecoin-to-millions-of-crypto-wallet-users</guid></item><item><title>加密货币兄弟似乎在逃避向美国国税局报告销售情况</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-14/crypto-bros-appear-to-be-dodging-reporting-sales-to-the-irs</link><description>一份新报告表明，很多人可能没有向美国国税局报告加密货币持有情况。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iXcegfz3ZNQ4/v15/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-14/crypto-bros-appear-to-be-dodging-reporting-sales-to-the-irs</guid></item><item><title>在伊朗乐观情绪中，比特币测试交易区间的高端</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/bitcoin-climbs-to-four-week-high-on-hopes-of-us-iran-peace-talks</link><description>由于对美国可以与伊朗达成协议以结束冲突的乐观情绪，风险资产上涨，比特币趋向两个多月交易区间的高端。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCYQ_y689Ysc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 01:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/bitcoin-climbs-to-four-week-high-on-hopes-of-us-iran-peace-talks</guid></item></channel></rss>